Features:
- Arena Regions
- Randomized Chests (Defined places)
- Reset Regions
- Donator Perks
- Lobby System
- Specified Arena Spawns
- Sponsor System (Using Money)
- Spectator System
- Currency System (By Winning and Donations)
- Time Limit
- Natural Disasters
- Grace Period

Perks:
- Cloak: As long as Player does not move they may remain Invisible
- Hunter: Start with Animal Compainion
- Beast-man: Animals ignore Player
- Third Eye: "Sense" Players near you but lack the ability to use weapons
- Fear-monger: Able to let out a scream that stuns nearby players